<span style="font-weight: bold;"><br>
The back story:&nbsp; </span>Once I had decided to expand to games
with more than 2 players, Medina was high on my list because it is
essentially an abstract game disguised as a euro.&nbsp; I researched it
by playing a few games, turn based, on ludagora.net, and I got lucky on
EBay to get an actual copy for a reasonable price.<br>
